{"tid":833636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩：中國人羨慕我們","createTime":"2018-09-23T15:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T02:41:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12c6e41e94ef993c0cffbc455eaa5766469b6c51","tid":833636,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:55:57.000Z","msg":"北韓領導人金正恩與南韓總統文在寅20日登上北韓國境內的長白山，共同眺望天池景致，金正恩竟公開對中國酸言酸語「中國人羨慕我們，因為他們到不了天池邊，但我們可以」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，第3次「文金會」的第3天，南、北韓領袖共同於上午10點20分攻上長白山的天池，並在現場對媒體做出牽手、比愛心等動作拍照，金正恩此時指出，中國人無法到達天池另端旁欣賞美麗景觀，對於朝鮮民族能夠做到這點感到相當欽羨。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩且說，許多南韓民眾會藉由中國國境爬上長白山，藉此接近靠近北韓的天池，文在寅則期許南韓民眾有朝一日能透過北韓登上長白山，文在寅也當場挽袖拉褲，穿著皮鞋走進天池，拿出預藏好的玻璃瓶蹲下汲取天池水源，景象也被媒體拍攝下來。<br />\n<br />\n中國原擁有長白山地區主權，但北韓在1948年成立共產政權後，多次向中方討取部分長白山與天池區域做為領土，於是中國前總理周恩來在1962年率眾前往平壤，與北韓簽署《中朝邊界條約》，同意將約一半面積的天池與部分長白山領域割讓給北韓，也就是目前的中國、北韓邊境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2560071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2560071&d=uHxJ9n78131ewW8ZY7XB1QIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=764459c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2560071&h=b71f79ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2560071</a>"},{"pid":"66b033c4c12fd72373ed5e3131ed274efd174fc4","tid":833636,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"牙金好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950789ae4f0da90469055d1c3d8c756cac7bc138","tid":833636,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaebaae456bbab344b1588149b89866b5648a9f","tid":833636,"uid":37220,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"中國原擁有長白山地區主權，但北韓在1948年成立共產政權後，多次向中方討取部分長白山與天池區域做為領土，於是中國前總理周恩來在1962年率眾前往平壤，與北韓簽署《中朝邊界條約》，同意將約一半面積的天池與部分長白山領域割讓給北韓，也就是目前的中國、北韓邊境。<br />\n<br />\n自古以來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1267d6d2f307a4652e8c9d6946bbe6fcd14286","tid":833636,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:49:59.000Z","msg":"不可分割<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412e3e3c688706bee352e01c27d9e8e76d655704","tid":833636,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5c6988e206664952d57a8497c3d62497dbc384","tid":833636,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d6d3cb5836fed3bc72540beb81b2aeb4d4b603","tid":833636,"uid":53466,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4abcfb14e44a22895ca0a89746201645f22737c8","tid":833636,"uid":79839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"以前做中國隻狗 依家痴下美國南韓咬番中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵啦"},{"pid":"5fb318a200a4924303134b7ebbbb3078273befda","tid":833636,"uid":2223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"金仔: 終於唔使睇中國人臉色！"},{"pid":"204ab8c5855010c8b448797b2fd4992a1d2b1913","tid":833636,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:24:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94af25a9eae9e4543cd4a72865b5d0e25ab76a0d","tid":833636,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:38:20.000Z","m